:"nathan-pharma-sliding-banner.jpg","url":"https://company.pharmahopers.com/nathan-pharma-private-limited"},{"id":96,"title":"Swastik Lifesciences","image":"swastik-life-science-sliding-banner.jpg","url":"https://company.pharmahopers.com/swastik-lifesciences"}],"meta":{"description":"PharmaHopers (Pharmaceutical B2B Marketplace) - Visit PharmaHopers to Get pharma B2B leads from genuine buyers \u0026 Suppliers. 6000+ product range present. ","title":"Pharmaceutical Companies B2B Marketplace \u0026 Directory | PharmaHopers "},"footer_text":"\u003ch4\u003eAbout PharmaHopers (Pharmaceutical B2B Marketplace \u0026amp; Online Pharma Directory)\u003c/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/\"\u003ePharmaHopers\u003c/a\u003e is a comprehensive B2B Pharmaceutical marketplace in India, where you can find top-rated \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/pharma-manufacturing\"\u003ePharmaceutical companies\u003c/a\u003e in India that deal in \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/pharma-franchise-pcd\"\u003ePCD Pharma Franchise\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/monopoly-pcd-pharma-franchise\"\u003eMonopoly Pharma Franchise\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/pharma-third-party-manufacturing\"\u003eThird-Party Manufacturing,\u003c/a\u003e and more. The idea for launching struck our minds in December 2016. This portal is run by a team of experienced professionals who have been serving the pharmaceutical industry by providing digital solutions for the past 12+ years. We have more that 1000+ vendors listed in multiple categories on our portal. You can find all types of \u003ca title=\"Cosmetic Manufacturers\" href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/cosmetics-and-personal-care\"\u003eCosmetic Manufacturers\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca title=\"Nutraceutical Manufacturers\" href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/nutraceutical-product-manufacturer\"\u003eNutraceutical Manufacturers\u003c/a\u003e, and Derma manufacturers having WHO GMP-certified units.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch6\u003eWhat makes us launch PharmaHopers?\u003c/h6\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAfter working for many years in the Pharmaceutical industry, we came to realize that the market area of this industry is vast. But due to mismanagement, a lack of enough resources, or less online awareness of pharmaceutical firms, causes damage in terms of sales as well as other branding aspects. Here is the list of problems that are analyzed by us\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOnline Awareness:\u003c/strong\u003e The First thing analyzed by us is that there are several \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/pharma-manufacturing\"\u003ePharma companies\u003c/a\u003e that provide medicine franchises do not have good online awareness. We are not talking about the top one, but we are talking about the other bunch of people who have less budget. So in this portal, you can get leads at a very low cost. You can check our \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pricing\"\u003emembership packages\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMismanagement of Resources:\u003c/strong\u003e The second and most important thing we have seen in the pharma industry is the mismanagement of resources. Since online awareness is a must so every Pharma franchise company is now focused on increasing its brand awareness online. But due to mismanagement, they are not using the resources properly, which can increase their business by 200%. So if you buy PharmaHopers, then we have a complete process where our experts help you in providing the resources that help you in increasing your conversion.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLess Team:\u003c/strong\u003e The third and last thing that was analyzed by us is the team size. This thing we have seen in the companies that are on the verge of making online awareness very quickly, but due to a smaller team, they lose the opportunity to convert that lead into your customer.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eHow PharmaHopers Portal work?\u003c/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWell we work on a model to provide you genuine buyers and sellers of the pharmaceutical industry. We have listed several categories in the portal which the buyer can choose accordingly and the seller can get the relevant lead. From the Buyers point of view, we have listed the top-rated pharmaceutical companies, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/pharma-third-party-manufacturing\"\u003ethird-party Manufacturing Pharma companies\u003c/a\u003e and other different product categories so that they can get the genuine company.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFrom the seller's point of view, we assure them that the inquiries that they get from the buyers are genuine. We bring buyers to our portal with the help of digital marketing techniques, which include paid advertisements and free advertisements on search engines and top social media platforms. Also from a seller's point of view, each company is provided with the log-in panel where they can check the new leads regularly and choose according to their vacant locations.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch6\u003eOur Major Categories\u003c/h6\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou'll find several business categories related to Pharma in our portal. But \u003ca href=\"https://www.pharmahopers.com/pharma/business-opportunities\"\u003ePharma Franchise Opportunity\u003c/a\u003e, Third-party manufacturing are our major ones. Since the pharma franchise model in the pharmaceutical industry is in huge demand and has less risk so more people are looking for a Pharma Franchise. So, due to this, our major category is PCD Franchise. Secondly, in India, there are several third-party pharma manufacturers who are exporting or manufacturing the products. So this becomes our second major category. But at PharmaHopers, you can find franchises for different ranges, types, classifications and as well as all manufacturers serving in multiple categories.\u003c/p\u003e","isMobileDevice":false,"customer_mobile":null,"pharma_product_list_cat":[{"title":"Cough Syrup List","slug":"cough-syrup-list"},{"title":"Antacid Medicine List","slug":"antacid-medicine-list"},{"title":"Antibiotic List","slug":"antibiotic-list"},{"title":"Eye Drops List","slug":"eye-drops-list"},{"title":"PCD Pharma Product List","slug":"pcd-pharma-product-list"},{"title":"Derma Product List","slug":"derma-product-list"},{"title":"Dental Product List","slug":"dental-product-list"},{"title":"Orthopedic Product List","slug":"orthopedic-product-list"},{"title":"Gynae Product List","slug":"gynae-product-list"},{"title":"Critical Care Product List","slug":"critical-care-product-list"},{"title":"Ayurvedic Product List","slug":"ayurvedic-product-list"},{"title":"Veterinary Product List","slug":"veterinary-product-list"},{"title":"Cardiac Diabetic Product List","slug":"cardiac-diabetic-product-list"},{"title":"Neuropsychiatry Product List","slug":"neuropsychiatry-product-list"},{"title":"Nephrology Product List","slug":"nephrology-product-list"},{"title":"Urology Product List","slug":"urology-product-list"},{"title":"Nutraceutical Product List","slug":"nutraceutical-product-list"},{"title":"Cosmetic Product List","slug":"cosmetic-product-list"}]}},"page":"/","query":{},"buildId":"EvRRqhHTPay_JopBxEd9c","isFallback":false,"customServer":true,"gip":true}</script><script nomodule="" src="/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-06d31ffa4dce26d67aef.js"></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/webpack-50bee04d1dc61f8adf5b.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/framework.c77c3085fdb94921e715.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/commons.60c12d91b2ad09f31f80.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/f6078781a05fe1bcb0902d23dbbb2662c8d200b3.3be2be1b185513095542.js" async=""></script><script src="/_next/static/chunks/main-739f9592e5e3625e9fea.js" as